<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.217679>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Aedeagi of Cystocnemis spp. in dorsal and lateral view. 5, С. concolor (Saur Mountain Range, Karaungir river valley); 6, C. discoidea discoidea (Eastern Kazakhstan, Ul’binsk); 7, C. zintshenkoi sp. nov., holotype (Eastern Kazakhstan, Bukombai Mts.); 8, C. levmedvedevi sp. nov., holotype (W Mongolia, Hovd aimag, Arshantyn- Nuruu Mts.); 9, С. (Entomomela) oirata, lectotype (Mongolian Altai, Sagsai river valley); 10, С. (Entomomela) arnoldii, holotype (Mongolian Altai, Munkh-Khairkhan Mts.). Scale bar— 1.0 mm. (5, 6, 9, 10 — from Mikhailov 2013; 7, 8 — orig.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/217679/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

